FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get Fit with Our Gym App
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our fitness companion
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides a comprehensive suite of features to help you achieve your fitness goals. From workout routines and exercise tracking to nutrition planning and progress monitoring, we've got you covered.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Getting started is easy! Simply download the app, create your profile, and set your fitness goals. Our intuitive interface will guide you through the process of customizing your workout and nutrition plans.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I access the app on multiple devices?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our app seamlessly syncs across all your devices, ensuring that your fitness data is always up-to-date and accessible, no matter where you are.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the app suitable for all fitness levels?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, our app caters to individuals of all fitness levels, from beginners to advanced athletes. We offer a wide range of workout options and customizable settings to accommodate your specific needs and abilities.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do you offer any additional resources or support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Certainly! In addition to our comprehensive app features, we provide a wealth of educational resources, including workout tutorials, nutrition guides, and expert advice from certified fitness professionals. Our dedicated support team is also available to assist you with any questions or concerns.

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Fitness App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What kind of workouts does the app offer?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides a wide variety of workout routines tailored for different fitness goals like building muscle, losing weight, increasing endurance, and improving flexibility. You'll find workouts for the gym, home, or outdoors using weights, resistance bands, bodyweight exercises, and more.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I create my own custom workout plans?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! One of the key features is the ability to build your own personalized workout programs from our exercise database. You can mix and match exercises, set rep ranges, rest times, and schedule workout days according to your preferences.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Does the app track my progress over time?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, the app allows you to log your workouts and track metrics like weight lifted, reps completed, and exercise time. You can view progress charts and personal records to see how you're improving and sustaining your fitness journey.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I connect with friends or find an online fitness community?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app has social features that enable you to connect with friends, join groups based on similar goals, and participate in fun challenges. You can share accomplishments, motivate each other, and be part of an engaged fitness community.
